---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Legendarios GYM · Gimnasio en el Centro de Mérida"
  description="⭐ 4.7 con 86 reseñas en Google. Variedad de máquinas, rutinas que sí funcionan y un coach que no te suelta. Gimnasio en el Centro de Mérida. Escríbenos por WhatsApp."
  slug="legendarios-gym-merida"
  ogImage="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_1.jpg"
  fonts="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bruno+Ace&family=Rubik:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
  favicon="👑"
  themeColor="#2e1065"
  whatsapp={"https://wa.me/19999707130"}
  telefono={"999 970 7130"}
  mapsUrl={"https://maps.google.com/?cid=886195260300356566&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA"}
>
  <main class="lg">

    <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
    <header class="hero">
      <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
        <img src="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_1.jpg" alt="" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" />
      </div>
      <svg class="crown-mark" viewBox="0 0 200 120" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M20 100 L20 55 L50 80 L70 40 L100 75 L130 40 L150 80 L180 55 L180 100 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="6" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="20" cy="50" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="70" cy="35" r="9" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="70" r="7" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="130" cy="35" r="9" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="180" cy="50" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <rect x="20" y="100" width="160" height="14" rx="3" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="wrap hero-wrap">
        <p class="kicker reveal">Gimnasio · Centro, Mérida</p>
        <h1 class="poster reveal">
          <span class="l1">Legendarios</span>
          <span class="l2">GYM</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="by-line reveal">by Xhin</p>
        <p class="tagline reveal">Variedad de máquinas, rutinas que <strong>sí funcionan</strong> y un coach que no te suelta hasta que las dominas.</p>

        <a class="chip reveal" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=886195260300356566&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="star" aria-hidden="true">★</span> 4.7 · 86 reseñas en Google
        </a>

        <div class="cta-row reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-solid" href="https://wa.me/19999707130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 0-8.6 15.1L2 22l5.1-1.3A10 10 0 1 0 12 2zm0 18.2c-1.5 0-3-.4-4.3-1.2l-.3-.2-3 .8.8-2.9-.2-.3A8.2 8.2 0 1 1 12 20.2zm4.6-6.1c-.3-.1-1.5-.7-1.7-.8-.2-.1-.4-.1-.6.1-.2.3-.6.8-.8 1-.1.2-.3.2-.5.1a6.7 6.7 0 0 1-3.4-3c-.3-.4 0-.5.2-.7l.4-.5c.1-.2.2-.3.3-.5v-.5c0-.1-.5-1.3-.7-1.8-.2-.5-.4-.4-.6-.4h-.5c-.2 0-.5.1-.7.3-.3.3-.9.9-.9 2.2s.9 2.5 1 2.7c.1.2 1.8 2.8 4.4 3.9.6.3 1.1.4 1.5.6.6.2 1.2.2 1.6.1.5-.1 1.5-.6 1.7-1.2.2-.6.2-1.1.2-1.2l-.4-.3z"/></svg>
            Escríbenos por WhatsApp
          </a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=886195260300356566&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="18" height="18" aria-hidden="true" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2a7 7 0 0 0-7 7c0 5.2 7 13 7 13s7-7.8 7-13a7 7 0 0 0-7-7zm0 9.5A2.5 2.5 0 1 1 12 6.5a2.5 2.5 0 0 1 0 5z"/></svg>
            Cómo llegar
          </a>
        </div>

        <dl class="datos reveal">
          <div><dt>4.7<span aria-hidden="true">★</span></dt><dd>calificación real en Google</dd></div>
          <div><dt>86</dt><dd>reseñas de alumnos</dd></div>
          <div><dt>6 días</dt><dd>a la semana, desde las 6:00 am</dd></div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- ============ 01 QUIÉNES SOMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="nosotros">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal"><span class="mini-crown" aria-hidden="true">♛</span> 01 / Quiénes somos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Aquí se forjan <span class="gold">leyendas</span></h2>
        <div class="nosotros-grid">
          <div class="about reveal">
            <p>Somos <strong>Legendarios GYM</strong>, un gimnasio en el Centro de Mérida con la variedad de máquinas que hace falta para entrenar en serio — pesas, cardio y todo lo de en medio, sin pasarte la sesión esperando turno.</p>
            <p>El coach del gym —el mismo que le da nombre a la casa, <strong>by Xhin</strong>— arma las rutinas y no te suelta hasta que las dominas. Nuestros alumnos lo describen tal cual: "excelente coach", "todo muy profesional".</p>
            <p>El resto lo hace el ambiente: buen trato del personal, espacio y discos suficientes, y esa energía que se siente apenas entras. Ven a conocer el gym — te esperamos en el Centro.</p>
          </div>
          <figure class="foto-cred reveal">
            <img src="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_3.jpg" alt="El escudo de Legendarios GYM pintado en el muro del gimnasio, junto a uno de los coaches" loading="lazy" />
            <figcaption>El escudo de Legendarios, en el muro del gym</figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 02 QUÉ OFRECEMOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="instalaciones">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal"><span class="mini-crown" aria-hidden="true">♛</span> 02 / Qué ofrecemos</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Todo lo que pide tu rutina</h2>
        <div class="ofrece-grid">
          <ol class="servicios reveal">
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
              <div><h3>Variedad de máquinas</h3><p>Estaciones de pesas en buen estado y sin esperar turno — lo que más destacan nuestros alumnos.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
              <div><h3>Área de cardio</h3><p>Caminadoras y elípticas para calentar o cerrar la sesión.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
              <div><h3>Peso libre con discos de sobra</h3><p>Suficientes discos para no andar cargando pesas ajenas a media serie.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
              <div><h3>Rutinas con coach</h3><p>Seguimiento real: te arman el plan y te corrigen la técnica.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
              <div><h3>Buen ambiente y trato</h3><p>Personal atento y un gym que se siente como equipo, no como membresía anónima.</p></div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="num" aria-hidden="true">06</span>
              <div><h3>Aceptamos tarjeta</h3><p>Para que no batalles con efectivo cada mes.</p></div>
            </li>
          </ol>
          <div class="ofrece-fotos">
            <img src="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_4.jpg" alt="Área de cardio de Legendarios GYM, con caminadoras y elípticas" loading="lazy" />
            <img src="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_2.jpg" alt="Área de pesas y máquinas de Legendarios GYM" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 03 PRUEBA SOCIAL ============ -->
    <section class="sec" id="resenas">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal"><span class="mini-crown" aria-hidden="true">♛</span> 03 / Lo que dicen en Google</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title rating-title reveal">
          <svg class="laurel laurel-l" viewBox="0 0 60 140" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M30 130 Q10 100 20 70 Q10 50 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"/><ellipse cx="16" cy="112" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-30 16 112)"/><ellipse cx="14" cy="92" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-20 14 92)"/><ellipse cx="16" cy="72" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-15 16 72)"/><ellipse cx="15" cy="52" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-10 15 52)"/><ellipse cx="18" cy="32" rx="9" ry="4.5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-5 18 32)"/></svg>
          <span class="gold">4.7 de 5</span> en 86 reseñas
          <svg class="laurel laurel-r" viewBox="0 0 60 140" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M30 130 Q10 100 20 70 Q10 50 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3"/><ellipse cx="16" cy="112" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-30 16 112)"/><ellipse cx="14" cy="92" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-20 14 92)"/><ellipse cx="16" cy="72" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-15 16 72)"/><ellipse cx="15" cy="52" rx="10" ry="5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-10 15 52)"/><ellipse cx="18" cy="32" rx="9" ry="4.5" fill="currentColor" transform="rotate(-5 18 32)"/></svg>
        </h2>
        <div class="reviews reveal">
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Buen Gym, variedad de maquinas , buenas rutinas , excelente ambiente»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Diego O.</strong><span>Hace 2 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Buena atención y excelente coach. Todo muy profesional.»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Nia Pinzón</strong><span>Hace 5 meses · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
          <figure class="rev">
            <p class="rev-stars" aria-label="5 estrellas">★★★★★</p>
            <blockquote>«Buen espacio para entrenar, las máquinas están en buen estado, suficientes discos, buen trato del personal 👏»</blockquote>
            <figcaption><strong>Abi Durán</strong><span>Hace un año · Google</span></figcaption>
          </figure>
        </div>
        <figure class="foto-ambiente reveal">
          <img src="/legendarios-gym-merida/img/foto_5.jpg" alt="Alumnos y coaches de Legendarios GYM en el gimnasio" loading="lazy" />
        </figure>
        <div class="center reveal">
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=886195260300356566&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Leer más reseñas en Google</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ 04 UBICACIÓN Y HORARIOS ============ -->
    <section class="sec sec-panel" id="ubicacion">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="sec-kicker reveal"><span class="mini-crown" aria-hidden="true">♛</span> 04 / Dónde entrenar</p>
        <h2 class="sec-title reveal">Centro de <span class="gold">Mérida</span></h2>
        <div class="ubica reveal">
          <div class="ubica-info">
            <p class="dir">Calle 73a #497, Centro<br />C. 58 entre 56 y 58<br />97000 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
            <a class="btn btn-solid btn-sm" href="https://maps.google.com/?cid=886195260300356566&g_mp=CiVnb29nbGUubWFwcy5wbGFjZXMudjEuUGxhY2VzLkdldFBsYWNlEAIYBCAA" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Abrir en Google Maps</a>
            <h3 class="horario-titulo">Horario del gym</h3>
            <table class="horarios">
              <tbody>
                <tr data-dia="1"><th scope="row">Lunes</th><td>6:00–22:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="2"><th scope="row">Martes</th><td>6:00–22:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="3"><th scope="row">Miércoles</th><td>6:00–22:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="4"><th scope="row">Jueves</th><td>6:00–22:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="5"><th scope="row">Viernes</th><td>6:00–22:30</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="6"><th scope="row">Sábado</th><td>7:00–14:00</td></tr>
                <tr data-dia="0"><th scope="row">Domingo</th><td>Cerrado</td></tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <div class="mapa">
            <iframe
              src="https://www.google.com/maps?q=Legendarios%20GYM%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Calle%2073a%20%23497%20centro%2C%20C.%2058%20entre%2056%20y%2058%2C%20Centro%2C%2097000%20M%C3%A9rida%2C%20Yuc.%2C%20M%C3%A9xico&output=embed"
              title="Mapa: Legendarios GYM en el Centro de Mérida"
              loading="lazy"
              referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
              allowfullscreen></iframe>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ CTA FINAL ============ -->
    <section class="banda">
      <svg class="crown-mark crown-mark--banda" viewBox="0 0 200 120" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M20 100 L20 55 L50 80 L70 40 L100 75 L130 40 L150 80 L180 55 L180 100 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="6" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="20" cy="50" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="70" cy="35" r="9" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="100" cy="70" r="7" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="130" cy="35" r="9" fill="currentColor"/>
        <circle cx="180" cy="50" r="8" fill="currentColor"/>
        <rect x="20" y="100" width="160" height="14" rx="3" fill="currentColor"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="wrap">
        <h2 class="banda-title">¿Listo para tu leyenda?</h2>
        <p class="banda-sub">Variedad de máquinas, rutinas que funcionan y un coach que no te suelta. Empieza hoy.</p>
        <div class="cta-row">
          <a class="btn btn-dark" href="https://wa.me/19999707130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp directo</a>
          <a class="btn btn-dark-ghost" href="tel:+529999707130">Llamar · 999 970 7130</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FOOTER ============ -->
    <footer class="pie">
      <div class="wrap">
        <p class="pie-logo">Legendarios GYM</p>
        <p class="pie-dato">Gimnasio · Calle 73a #497, Centro, 97000 Mérida, Yucatán</p>
        <p class="pie-dato"><a href="tel:+529999707130">999 970 7130</a> · <a href="https://wa.me/19999707130" target="_blank" rel="noopener">WhatsApp</a> · <a href="https://www.facebook.com/legendariosgymbyxhinos/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a></p>
        <p class="pie-mini">Lunes a viernes 6:00–22:30 · Sábado 7:00–14:00 · Domingo cerrado</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>

  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline>
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "HealthClub",
    "name": "Legendarios GYM",
    "telephone": "+529999707130",
    "url": "https://demos.ivang.mx/legendarios-gym-merida",
    "address": {
      "@type": "PostalAddress",
      "streetAddress": "Calle 73a #497 centro, C. 58 entre 56 y 58",
      "addressLocality": "Mérida",
      "addressRegion": "Yucatán",
      "postalCode": "97000",
      "addressCountry": "MX"
    },
    "aggregateRating": {
      "@type": "AggregateRating",
      "ratingValue": "4.7",
      "reviewCount": "86"
    },
    "openingHours": ["Mo-Fr 06:00-22:30", "Sa 07:00-14:00"]
  }
  </script>

  <style is:global>
    :root {
      --ink: #2e1065;
      --deep: #200a4c;
      --panel: #3b1d7a;
      --gold: #eab308;
      --gold-light: #f4cf4e;
      --bone: #f5f0e6;
      --muted: #c7bce0;
      --line: rgba(245, 240, 230, 0.16);
      --display: "Bruno Ace", "Arial Narrow", sans-serif;
      --body: "Rubik", system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--bone);
      font-family: var(--body);
      font-size: 17px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: clip;
    }

    .lg ::selection { background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); }
    .lg a:focus-visible,
    .lg .btn:focus-visible {
      outline: 3px solid var(--gold);
      outline-offset: 3px;
    }

    .wrap { max-width: 1040px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .gold { color: var(--gold); }

    /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: calc(100vh - 38px);
      min-height: calc(100svh - 38px);
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 56px 0 44px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .hero-bg img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 30%;
    }
    .hero-bg::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(32, 10, 76, 0.55) 0%, rgba(32, 10, 76, 0.75) 45%, var(--ink) 96%),
        radial-gradient(900px 500px at 82% 4%, rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.22), transparent 60%);
    }
    .crown-mark {
      position: absolute;
      top: 6%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      width: min(560px, 92vw);
      height: auto;
      color: var(--gold);
      opacity: 0.1;
      z-index: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-wrap { position: relative; z-index: 2; }

    .kicker {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.24em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .poster {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      line-height: 0.92;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .poster .l1 {
      font-size: clamp(44px, 12.5vw, 108px);
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      text-shadow: 0 0 46px rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.35);
    }
    .poster .l2 {
      font-size: clamp(30px, 8.5vw, 70px);
      color: transparent;
      -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--bone);
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }
    @supports not (-webkit-text-stroke: 2px black) {
      .poster .l2 { color: var(--bone); }
    }
    .by-line {
      margin: 10px 0 0;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .tagline {
      font-size: clamp(18px, 4.4vw, 23px);
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--bone);
      max-width: 36ch;
      margin: 22px 0 18px;
    }
    .tagline strong { color: var(--gold); font-weight: 500; }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--bone);
      text-decoration: none;
      background: rgba(245, 240, 230, 0.05);
    }
    .chip .star { color: var(--gold); }
    .chip:hover { border-color: var(--gold); }

    .cta-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 12px; margin: 26px 0 0; }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 16px 26px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: transform 0.15s ease, background-color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.97); }
    .btn-solid { background: var(--gold); color: var(--ink); }
    .btn-solid:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
    .btn-ghost { border: 2px solid var(--line); color: var(--bone); }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }
    .btn-sm { font-size: 14px; padding: 13px 20px; }

    .datos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin: 42px 0 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      padding-top: 20px;
    }
    .datos dt {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: clamp(22px, 5.6vw, 34px);
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .datos dt span { color: var(--gold); }
    .datos dd { margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.4; }

    /* ---------- ICONOS FIRMA ---------- */
    .mini-crown { color: var(--gold); font-size: 15px; margin-right: 4px; }
    .laurel { width: 30px; height: 70px; color: var(--gold); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .laurel-r { transform: scaleX(-1); }

    /* ---------- SECCIONES ---------- */
    .sec { padding: 76px 0; }
    .sec-panel { background: var(--panel); }
    .sec-kicker {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 13px;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 7.6vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1.02;
      margin: 0 0 30px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .rating-title {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 14px;
      text-align: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nosotros-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 30px; }
    .about p { max-width: 62ch; margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--muted); }
    .about strong { color: var(--bone); font-weight: 500; }
    .foto-cred { margin: 0; }
    .foto-cred img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: block;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }
    .foto-cred figcaption {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* ---------- SERVICIOS / OFRECEMOS ---------- */
    .ofrece-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    .servicios {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 0;
    }
    .servicios li {
      display: flex;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: baseline;
      padding: 18px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    }
    .servicios li:last-child { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .servicios .num {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 26px;
      color: var(--gold);
      min-width: 46px;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .servicios h3 {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 19px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 4px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .servicios p { margin: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 15px; }
    .ofrece-fotos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
      align-content: start;
    }
    .ofrece-fotos img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      min-height: 160px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 34px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    }

    /* ---------- RESEÑAS ---------- */
    .reviews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 18px;
      margin: 0 0 34px;
    }
    .rev {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--deep);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 22px 22px 20px;
    }
    .rev-stars {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
    }
    .rev blockquote {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .rev figcaption {
      margin: 0;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .rev figcaption strong {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 16px;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .rev figcaption span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
    .center { text-align: center; }
    .foto-ambiente { margin: 0 0 34px; }
    .foto-ambiente img {
      width: 100%;
      max-height: 420px;
      object-fit: cover;
      object-position: center 20%;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: block;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 44px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    /* ---------- UBICACIÓN ---------- */
    .ubica { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
    .dir { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0 0 16px; color: var(--bone); }
    .horario-titulo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 19px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      margin: 30px 0 10px;
      color: var(--bone);
    }
    .horarios { width: 100%; max-width: 420px; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 15px; }
    .horarios th, .horarios td { padding: 9px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); text-align: left; }
    .horarios th { font-weight: 500; color: var(--bone); }
    .horarios td { color: var(--muted); text-align: right; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th, .horarios tr.hoy td { color: var(--ink); background: var(--gold); font-weight: 600; }
    .horarios tr.hoy th::after {
      content: "hoy";
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--gold);
      border-radius: 4px;
      padding: 2px 7px;
      margin-left: 10px;
      vertical-align: 1px;
    }
    .mapa iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 300px;
      border: 0;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: block;
      filter: saturate(0.85) contrast(1.02);
    }

    /* ---------- CTA FINAL ---------- */
    .banda {
      position: relative;
      background: var(--gold);
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: 64px 0;
      text-align: center;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .crown-mark--banda {
      color: var(--ink);
      opacity: 0.08;
      top: -10%;
    }
    .banda .wrap { position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .banda-title {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: clamp(32px, 7.6vw, 56px);
      line-height: 1;
      margin: 0 0 14px;
    }
    .banda-sub { margin: 0 auto 26px; max-width: 42ch; font-weight: 400; }
    .banda .cta-row { justify-content: center; }
    .btn-dark { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bone); }
    .btn-dark:hover { background: var(--deep); }
    .btn-dark-ghost { border: 2px solid rgba(46, 16, 101, 0.5); color: var(--ink); }
    .btn-dark-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ink); }

    /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
    .pie {
      padding: 44px 0 96px;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
      text-align: center;
      background: var(--deep);
    }
    .pie-logo {
      font-family: var(--display);
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 24px;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      color: var(--gold);
      margin: 0 0 10px;
    }
    .pie-dato { margin: 4px 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14.5px; }
    .pie-dato a { color: var(--bone); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold); }
    .pie-dato a:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .pie-mini { margin: 14px 0 0; color: #8f81b3; font-size: 12.5px; }

    /* ---------- REVEAL (solo con JS) ---------- */
    html.js .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    html.js .reveal.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

    /* ---------- DESKTOP ---------- */
    @media (min-width: 760px) {
      .sec { padding: 108px 0; }
      .nosotros-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; align-items: center; gap: 44px; }
      .ofrece-grid { grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr; align-items: start; }
      .ofrece-fotos { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .reviews { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); align-items: start; }
      .ubica { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr; align-items: start; }
      .mapa iframe { height: 420px; }
    }
  </style>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var d = document;
      d.documentElement.classList.add('js');

      // Resaltar el día de hoy en la tabla de horarios
      var hoy = new Date().getDay(); // 0 = domingo
      var fila = d.querySelector('.horarios tr[data-dia="' + hoy + '"]');
      if (fila) fila.classList.add('hoy');

      // Scroll-reveal (mejora progresiva)
      var els = d.querySelectorAll('.reveal');
      if ('IntersectionObserver' in window) {
        var io = new IntersectionObserver(function (entries) {
          entries.forEach(function (e) {
            if (e.isIntersecting) {
              e.target.classList.add('in');
              io.unobserve(e.target);
            }
          });
        }, { threshold: 0.12, rootMargin: '0px 0px -8% 0px' });
        els.forEach(function (el) { io.observe(el); });
      } else {
        els.forEach(function (el) { el.classList.add('in'); });
      }
    })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
